First is a family dinner.
Next is Puko telling Retsuko that a baby is...
body:
So here’s an @kingdomofkitten Ikari-verse mega collection!

First is a family dinner.

Next is Puko telling Retsuko that a baby is the ultimate ball and chain. But she still likes the kid.

Last is teen Ikari and his friends, Ikari is playing dark souls-esque game, Kim’s is looking at his new Rider belt and Nezumi is reminding them about thier test on the Sengoku era.
